      "text": [
        " الْحَجُّ فَرْضٌ عَلَى أَهْلِ الْجِدَةِ فِي كُلِّ عَامٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Muhammad Bin Ahmad, from Yaqoub Bin Yazeed, from Ibn Abu Umer, from Abu Jreer Al Qummy, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The Hajj is Necessitated upon the people of Al-Jeddah during every year’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "8. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from Ya’qub ibn Yazid from ibn abu ‘Umayr from abu Jarir al- Qummiy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Performing al-Hajj is obligatory upon people of Jaddah every year.’” "
        ]
      }
